data.description: Amazing 2022 manufactured home, situated on a permanent foundation, offers a comfortable and contemporary living space on a generous 2.2762-acre lot. Boasting a spacious 1584 square feet, the home features a welcoming open/split floor plan with high ceilings throughout. The kitchen is equipped with a breakfast bar, stainless steel and black Whirlpool appliances, and includes a refrigerator and washer and dryer. Additional interior highlights comprise recessed lighting, laminate flooring, and a separate dining room area. The residence incorporates modern elements such as brush nickel hardware, double pane Low-E windows, central air conditioning, and a window swamp cooler. The three-bedroom, two-bathroom layout includes a master bedroom with dual large closets and an expansive ensuite bathroom featuring dual sinks, ample cabinets, and a walk-in shower. A separate laundry room, with access to the fenced backyard, enhances convenience. The property provides versatility with its vast lot, suitable for parking various vehicles and accommodating potential additions like a garage, workshop, or ADU (Buyer to Verify). Located in the Snowline School District with low property taxes, this home combines modern comforts with ample space and numerous possibilities for customization.
